Package cs2030s.fp

Class InfiniteList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs2030s.fp.InfiniteList<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    InfiniteList.EmptyList
    public class InfiniteList<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements a Lazy Infinite List.

    The elements of the list are lazy, and will only be evaluated when called upon. The list is recursively defined, with a special tail "EmptyList" to denote the end of the list.

    CS2030S Lab7 AY20/21 Semester 2
